node.text:
Who wants to see a great product in a review with a twist of fun?

A great alternative to MagSafe Charger that allows you to use your iPhone 12 while placing it still on the desk and charging it at the same time. 

Thanks to @esrgear.fr & @esrgear_official for sending the review unit. 

Full Video is on our YouTube Channel.

#iPhone12 #iPhone12ProMax #fun #iPhone12Pro #iPhone12Mini #Apple #iPhone #MagSafe #MagSafeCharger

⌚️ Apple Watch Series 7 Will NOT be released in September according to recent information obtained first by Nikkei and corroborated by Bloomberg. 

📆Apple Watch Series 7 is still expected to be announced during Apple’s September Event but the release is expected some time in November.

Apple admitted (!) its mistake with Safari in iOS 15

The new design with the web address bar being placed on the bottom of Safari in the first 5 betas of iOS 15 has been flawed and universally blamed by press and iOS users. 

The biggest issues aren’t related to our past habits. However, the UI elements of many websites are already placed on the bottom of each page making the coexistence with Safari almost unbearable. Banking apps or e-shops have been some of these affected apps. 

Apple listened (well done Apple!!!) and delivered a new option within the Safari settings that allows you to set the url bar either on top or the bottom. 

Where do you think it’s better, top or bottom?
